Cyber Claw:








Cyber Claw plowed down into the shore, with salt water dripping from her 
body. Her wounds, marked with blue stung with the strange water. She had 
never been at an ocean before. She bared with it, since she had endored 
worse pain that this. It wasn't worth whimpering about. She shook her body, 
spraying the salt water here and there. She didn't like the salty smell of 
this terrain. She preferred the forest.
